Isidumbu sitholwe ngonogada beReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa) ngoLwesibili ngo-7.31 ekuseni. Esitatimendeni seRusa ekhasini labo kwiFacebook, baveza ukuthi bathole ucingo obeluvela kumsebenzi wasegaraji obebabikela ngalesi sidumbu azithele phezu kwaso epaki. “Onogada bafike epaki bazithela phezu kwesidumbu endaweni evulekile. Umufi obebukeka eneminyaka eko-50 utholwe engazifakile izicathulo. Ubegqoke isikibha nesikhindi okusawolintshi. Ayaziwa imbangela yokufa kwakhe,” kusho iRusa.